data.description: Custom Built home by Crystal Creek Homes, the home offers primary bedroom down with en suite walk-in shower, Primary bath is ADA accessible as well entry doorways; three bedrooms and game room up, walk-in closets, gas log fireplace, three and a half baths, cook's dream kitchen with large island, lots of beautiful cabinets, large butler's pantry, laundry room, separate office, optional extra laundry room upstairs, plenty of storage and cabinets, Custom blinds, Generac generator, sprinkler system, enjoy the water view from your back covered patio, fenced back yard with gate access to the pond for fishing. Many restaurants, golf, boating, shopping and entertainment close by.  Easy access to Houston and Galveston for work, medical and shopping.
